overview.en: The CMFF is a decentralized block chain digital asset issued based on the Ethernet chain technology . The goal is to create a new business model based on block chain technology - digital internet entertainment model .
overview.zh: 摩根凤凰（CMFF）是基于以太坊技术发行的去中心化的区块链数字资产，其目标是打造一个全新基于区块链技术的商业模式-数位化互联网娱乐模式.
